MAPPING.DESCRIPTION:
Created By: CTS on July 5th 2017
This mapping will read the log file in xml format and will generate the Target File with SQL Queries used in the paricular Session
MAPPING.NAME: m_Informatica_Session_Log_SQL_Reader

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Using Sorter Transformation to sort the data based on Timestamp generated by Session log file
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: srt_Informatica_Session_Log_Reader

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Using Transaction Control transformation to generate the files based on file names
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: trns_Informatica_Session_Log_Reader

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Using Transaction Control transformation to generate the files based on file names
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: trns_Informatica_Session_Log_Stats_Reader

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Using Expression Transformation to Clenup the message column to get the particular SQL Query.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: exp_Informatica_Session_Log_Stats_Reader

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: decode(true, instr(message,'Table:')>0 AND instr(message,'view name')=0, 'Table_Stats_Check_Y', instr(message,'The index cache size that would hold [')>0,'Cache_Rows_Check_Y', instr(message,'Table:')>0 AND instr(message,'view name')>0, 'XML_Stats_Check_Y', substr(substr(message,instr(message,'End')),1,40)='End of output from Sorter Transformation','Srt_Stats_Check_Y' ,null )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_Row_Type_Check

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: decode(true, v_Row_Type_Check='Table_Stats_Check_Y', substr(message,instr(message,'[',1,3)+1,instr(message,']',1,3)-instr(message,'[',1,3)-1), v_Row_Type_Check='XML_Stats_Check_Y', substr(message,instr(message,'[',1,5)+1,instr(message,']',1,5)-instr(message,'[',1,5)-1), v_Row_Type_Check='Cache_Rows_Check_Y', substr(message,instr(message,'[')+1,instr(message,']')-instr(message,'[')-1), v_Row_Type_Check='Srt_Stats_Check_Y', substr(message,instr(message,' ',1,9)+1,instr(message,' ',1,10)-instr(message,' ',1,9)-1) , '0' )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_Output_Rows

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Validate XML Source
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: Validate only if DTD/Schema is present

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Filter Condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: (instr(message,'The index cache size that would hold [')>0) OR (substr(message,1,6)='Table:') OR substr(substr(message,instr(message,'End')),1,40)='End of output from Sorter Transformation'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION:
Filter transformation to filter the data based on message code. As of now we are using the below filter condition to filter the data.
1.Lookup transformation 2.SQ Instance 3. Mapping Name 4. Pre- SQL 5. Post SQL 6.SQL Transformation
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: flt_Informatica_Session_Log_Reader

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Filter Condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: (upper(substr(message,0,21))='LOOKUP TRANSFORMATION') OR (upper(substr(message,0,11))='SQ INSTANCE') OR (upper(substr(message,0,13))='MAPPING NAME:') OR (substr(message,0,25)='Executing pre-session SQL') OR (substr(message,0,26)='Executing post-session SQL') OR (instr(message,'Pre SQL')>0 and instr(message,'Starting')>0) OR (instr(message,'Post SQL')>0 and instr(message,'Starting')>0) OR (instr(message,'[Pre/Post Session Command] Started')>0) OR (severity=1) OR instr(message,'Initializing session [')>0 OR instr(message,'Repository Name:')>0 OR instr(message,'Folder:')>0 OR instr(message,'SQL UPDATE override statement:')>0 OR (instr(message,'End loading table [')>0 OR (instr(message,'Starting shell command')>0 and instr(message,'[Pre/Post Session Command]')=0) OR (instr(message,'The last SQL query to run was:')>0))

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Using Expression Transformation to Clenup the message column to get the particular SQL Query.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: exp_Informatica_Session_Log_Reader

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF((substr(message,0,25)='Executing pre-session SQL') OR (substr(message,0,26)='Executing post-session SQL') ,'Pre_Post_Sql_Query_Y','Pre_Post_Sql_Query_N')
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_Pre_Post_Sql_Query_Check

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(instr(message,'The last SQL query to run was:')>0,'SQL_Trans_Y','SQL_Trans_N')
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_Pmsql_SQL_Transformation_Check

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
decode(TRUE, v_Session_run_Details_Check='RUN_DEATILS_Y', 'Session Name : '||substr(message,instr(message,'[',1,1)+1,instr(message,']',1,1)-instr(message,'[',1,1)-1)||CHR(13)||CHR(10)||'Run Date and Time : '||substr(message,instr(message,'[',3,2)+1,instr(message,']',3,2)-instr(message,'[',3,2)-1), v_Repository_Details_Check='REPO_DEATILS_Y', REPLACESTR(0,REPLACESTR(0,message,']',''),'[',''), v_End_Loading='END_LOAD_Y', '-----------------------------------------------------------------'||CHR(13)||CHR(10)||'Target Table:'||substr(message,instr(message,'[')+1,instr(message,']')-instr(message,'[')-1)||CHR(13)||CHR(10)||'-----------------------------------------------------------------'||CHR(13)||CHR(10),
v_File_Commands='FILE_CMD_Y', '-----------------------------------------------------------------'||CHR(13)||CHR(10)||'File Commands :'||CHR(13)||CHR(10)||substr(message,instr(message,'[',2)+1,instr(message,'].',2)-instr(message,'[',2)-1)||CHR(13)||CHR(10)||'-----------------------------------------------------------------'||CHR(13)||CHR(10),
v_Query_Check='Query_Y', '-----------------------------------------------------------------'||CHR(13)||CHR(10)||substr(message,instr(message,'[')+1,instr(message,']')-instr(message,'[')-1)||':'||CHR(13)||CHR(10)||'-----------------------------------------------------------------'||CHR(13)||CHR(10)|| decode( true, instr(UPPER(message),'SQL QUERY')>0,REPLACESTR(0,substr(message,instr(UPPER(message),'SQL QUERY [')+11),']',''), instr(UPPER(message),'LOOKUP TRANSFORMATION')>0,REPLACESTR(0,substr(message,instr(UPPER(message),':',1,2)+2),']','') ),
v_Pmsql_SQL_Transformation_Check='SQL_Trans_Y', '-----------------------------------------------------------------'||CHR(13)||CHR(10)||'SQL Transformation Queries:'||CHR(13)||CHR(10)||'-----------------------------------------------------------------'||CHR(13)||CHR(10)||substr(message,instr(message,':')+1,instr(message,'database')-instr(message,':')-1)||CHR(13)||CHR(10) ,
v_Pre_Post_Sql_Table_Check='Pre_Post_Sql_Table_Y', '-----------------------------------------------------------------'||CHR(13)||CHR(10)||REPLACESTR(0,substr(message,instr(message,'P'),instr(message,']')-instr(message,'P'))||':','[',''), v_Pre_Post_Sql_Query_Check='Pre_Post_Sql_Query_Y', '-----------------------------------------------------------------'||CHR(13)||CHR(10)||substr(message,instr(message,':')+2), v_Pre_Post_Session_Cmd_Check='Pre_Post_Sess_Cmd_Y', '-----------------------------------------------------------------'||CHR(13)||CHR(10)||substr(message,instr(message,'[')+1,instr(message,']')-instr(message,'[')-1)||':'||CHR(13)||CHR(10)||'-----------------------------------------------------------------'||CHR(13)||CHR(10)||substr(message,instr(message,'[',2)+1,instr(message,'].',2)-instr(message,'[',2)-1), v_Target_Override_Check='Target_Override_Y', '-----------------------------------------------------------------'||CHR(13)||CHR(10)||substr(message,0,instr(message,':',2,2))||CHR(13)||CHR(10)||'-----------------------------------------------------------------'||CHR(13)||CHR(10)||substr(message,instr(message,':',2,2)+1)||CHR(13)||CHR(10),message)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_message
